nathan fillion ( ; born march 27 , 1971 ) is a canadian actor and voice actor best known for his role as richard castle on the abc series castle , as well as his earlier portrayal of the lead role of captain malcolm reynolds in the television series firefly and its feature film continuation , serenity .

tv title references : nathan fillion plays a mystery novelist with this last name ; he helps a female nyc police detective solve crimes

